00:07:43.980 --> 00:07:46.360 align:middle line:84%
Or if you calculate
that all out,

00:07:46.360 --> 00:07:49.040 align:middle line:84%
we could save a trillion
dollars annually.

00:07:49.040 --> 00:07:51.340 align:middle line:84%
So that means we would
have plenty-- collectively.

00:07:51.340 --> 00:07:54.920 align:middle line:84%
So we would have plenty of
money to do all those services

00:07:54.920 --> 00:07:58.770 align:middle line:84%
