nationalized the banks,

00:08:01.180 --> 00:08:05.510 align:middle line:84%
we could have all those
services and things to spare.

00:08:05.510 --> 00:08:08.430 align:middle line:84%
Or we could eliminate
income taxes.

00:08:08.430 --> 00:08:09.270 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: OK.

00:08:09.270 --> 00:08:10.760 align:middle line:84%
